high_descs: Turn left walk forward then turn right face the table
Pick up the spoon on the table beside the cabbage
Turn right and head to the sink cabinet
Open the sink cabinet put the spoon in the plate
Pick up the plate with spoon then close the cabinet
Turn left and head to the table
Put the plate with spoon on the table beside the cabbage
anns.task_desc: Put the plate with spoon on the table

high_descs: Turn around and hang a right at the wall to reach the large wooden table.
Pick up the spoon behind the head of lettuce on the table.
Turn right and walk to the cabinets under the sink ahead.
Open the lower left cabinet and put the spoon inside the wooden bowl.
Pick up the bowl with the spoon from inside the cabinet.
Turn around and take a right at the wall to face the wooden table.
Put the bowl with the spoon behind the head of lettuce and to the left of the silver pot on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a spoon on a table.

high_descs: Go to the large wooden table
Pick up the spoon
Go to the sink
Place the spoon in a bowl in the sink cabinet
Take the bowl out
Go to the large wooden table
Place the bowl down
anns.task_desc: Put a bowl with a spoon in it on a table
